Package org.hms.services.medicalrecord

Class ContactInformationTable

java.lang.Object
org.hms.entities.AbstractTable<ContactInformation>
org.hms.services.medicalrecord.ContactInformationTable
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ContactInformationTable extends AbstractTable<ContactInformation>
This class represents a table of contact information, providing functionality to manage, format, and render contact entries such as phone numbers and emails. It extends the AbstractTable class and operates on ContactInformation objects.
